reece}} [[Georgios Papandreou]]\nFile:Portrait Habib Bourguiba.jpg|{{flagicon|Tunisia}} '''[[Habib Bourguiba]]'''\nFile:Makarios_III_and_Robert_F._Wagner_NYWTS_cropped.jpg|{{flagicon|Cyprus}} '''[[Makarios III]]'''\nFile:Demirel_1976_cropped.jpg|{{flagicon|Turkey}} [[S\u00fcleyman Demirel]]\nFile:Inonu_Ismet.jpg|{{flagicon|Turkey}} [[\u0130smet \u0130n\u00f6n\u00fc]]\nFile:Anastasio_Somoza_Debayle.PNG|{{flagicon|Nicaragua}} [[Anastasio Somoza Debayle]]\nFile:King_Zahir_Shah_of_Afghanistan_in_1963.jpg|{{flagicon|Afghanistan|1931}} '''[[Mohammed Zahir Shah]]'''\nFile:King_Hassan_II.jpg|{{flagicon|Morocco}} [[Hassan II of Morocco|Hassan II]]\nFile:Anefo_911-6993_Aankomst_Koning_(cropped).jpg|{{flagicon|Thailand}} '''[[Bhumibol Adulyadej]]'''\nFile:Prince_Rainier_III.jpg|{{flagicon|Monaco}} '''[[Rainier III, Prince of Monaco|Rainier III]]'''\nFile:Jan de Quay 1962.jpg|{{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Jan de Quay]]\nFile:Piet de Jong 1970.jpg|{{flagicon|Netherlands}} [[Piet de Jong]]\nFile:Abd_al-Karim_Qasim_5.jpg|{{flagicon|Iraq}} [[Abd al-Karim Qasim]]\nFile:Imam_Ahmad_Hamid_al-Din.jpg|{{flagicon|Yemen|1927}} [[Ahmad bin Yahya]]\nFile:Trujillo_1952.jpg|{{flagicon|Dominican Republic}} [[Rafael Trujillo]]\nFile:Eduardo Frei Montalva en su escritorio de La Moneda.jpg|{{flagicon|Chile}} [[Eduardo Frei Montalva]]\nFile:Diosdado Macapagal photo.jpg|{{flagicon|Philippines|1936}} [[Diosdado Macapagal]]\nFile:Young_Dr_Banda.jpg|{{flagicon|Malawi}} [[Hastings Banda]]\nFile:Kenneth_Kaunda_1983-03-30.jpg|{{flagicon|Zambia}} [[Kenneth Kaunda]]\n</gallery>\n\n===Activists===\nSome Activist leaders of the 1960s period include:\n* [[Joan Baez]]\n* [[James Bevel]]\n* [[Bob Dylan]]\n* [[Lawrence Ferlinghetti]]\n* [[Allen Ginsberg]]\n* [[Dick Gregory]]\n* [[Abbie Hoffman]]\n* [[Barbara Jordan]]\n* [[Martin Luther King]]\n* [[Timothy Leary]]\n* [[John Lennon]]\n* [[Yoko Ono]]\t\n* [[Jerry Rubin]]\n* [[Mario Savio]]\n* [[Malcolm X]]\n* [[Gloria Steinem]]\n\n===Actors / Entertainers===\n{{Div col